title: Converse Ready, Set Get Lost: Mac DeMarco "Cooking Up Something Good" Live
description: Mac DeMarco is quickly establishing himself as Brooklyn's preeminent singer songwriter. The 22 year old and his band visited us at the Brooklyn Navy Yard and planted themselves amid the industrial chaos; what resulted was a warm and gorgeous version of "Cooking Up Something Good, " off his recently released record 2, for our Ready, Set Get Lost series.
